Prerequisites Google Cloud Project BigQuery API Enabled Cloud Storage Bucket Service account credentials with access to all above Mapbox Token GitHub Account and GitHub Token Steps Checkout Dekart from GitHub; navigate to project directory;
Create .npmrc file in the project directory with the following content and your github token
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN @dekart-xyz:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com This step is required because dekart is using github packages
Install frontend dependencies npm install Create and edit .
